{"tid":1487773,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"BNO平權重點係在港公民人數，唔係走佬救命草，咪亂割","createTime":"2019-08-19T11:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:26:27.000Z","uid":261705,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4c9253be28e34395e09f024447e97ec56800a08e","tid":1487773,"uid":261705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"平權轉BC後在港不列顛下式公民人數唔少<br />\nChīn&agrave;每一步要更小心，因為必上國際<br />\n呢個壓力係重點，唔好一平權就飛<br />\n一旦真係出事，大不列顛就名正言順出手救民<br />\n<br />\n不列顛出手救人行先，之後先再出走佬移民潮<br />\n效果先夠大<br />\n<br />\n實際上，大多數BNO都有上下家室，唔係咁易走，要走不列顛因為文化差異都未必係1st choice <br />\n<br />\n唔好覺得轉咗BC全部都自私即走，過三字頭真係唔係話走就走咁易"},{"pid":"fa5d46db760d1793fa251cfed9329b86ff35ea59","tid":1487773,"uid":278283,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:02:15.000Z","msg":"平權百利而無一害<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF468RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=90262df6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"bd35fd1a1cb0f6c79ae85fbe141e3aba846c5c3c","tid":1487773,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:07:18.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"6e5fe9ab34c32a8736154a4d6b4d2c684add5935","tid":1487773,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"878ccee7492ded1b261a5c6258d4ffdc3ba65e04","tid":1487773,"uid":170370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:56:29.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"c4be7a8ce135fa460cbd7a222641028bab112500","tid":1487773,"uid":231583,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:00:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BNO平權不嬲都唔代表要走<br />\n只係令更多人少咁d後顧之憂多條後路，更豁出去抗爭<br />\n香港係我地屋企，未到最後一刻點解要走？</span>"},{"pid":"155bade005a2b8b897584744c82640b10bb9