itions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n平權聯署，就差你一個簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0528c74a0d7dded073d7a6434b3964c1f3bcc1e","tid":1487773,"uid":303347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c9253be28e34395e09f024447e97ec56800a08e","tid":1487773,"uid":261705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"平權轉BC後在港不列顛下式公民人數唔少<br />\nChīn&agrave;每一步要更小心，因為必上國際<br />\n呢個壓力係重點，唔好一平權就飛<br />\n一旦真係出事，大不列顛就名正言順出手救民<br />\n<br />\n不列顛出手救人行先，之後先再出走佬移民潮<br />\n效果先夠大<br />\n<br />\n實際上，大多數BNO都有上下家室，唔係咁易走，要走不列顛因為文化差異都未必係1st choice <br />\n<br />\n唔好覺得轉咗BC全部都自私即走，過三字頭真係唔係話走就走咁易"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:43:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2e8adb6f3cebcd0c1da7017073f42eaa282b0483","tid":1487773,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:35:20.000Z","msg":"【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n脫支大行動<br />\n<br />\nPostal code 就打000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF468RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=90262df6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"650424cfcc9ccf45503ae5b84b1831bd6b414245","tid":1487773,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4ddec728713d7ad9ec402024906393f494815c","tid":1487773,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4be